libspectrum
------------------------------------------
libspectrum is a library designed to make the input and output of some ZX
Spectrum emulator files slightly easier.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.15-1
  libaudiofile1-0.3.4-1
  libbz2_1-1.0.6-2
  libgcrypt11-1.4.6-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.32.3-1
  zlib0-1.2.7-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-10-1
  automake-4-10
  binutils-2.22.51-2
  cygport-0.10.10-1
  gawk-4.0.1-1
  gcc4-core-4.5.3-3
  libtool-2.4-1
  make-3.82.90-1

Canonical website:
  http://fuse-emulator.sf.net/libspectrum.php

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/fuse-emulator/libspectrum-1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack libspectrum-1.0.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./libspectrum-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libspectrum-1.0.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libspectrum-1.0.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libspectrum8-1.0.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libspectrum-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libspectrum)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libspectrum.README
  /usr/share/doc/libspectrum/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libspectrum/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libspectrum/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libspectrum/HACKING/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libspectrum/README
  /usr/share/doc/libspectrum/THANKS

(libspectrum8)
  /usr/bin/cygspectrum-8.dll

(libspectrum-devel)
  /usr/include/libspectrum.h
  /usr/lib/libspectrum.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libspectrum.la
  /usr/share/man/man3/libspectrum.3.gz

